What is MAT?

It's the only evidence-based treatment for opioid use disorder.

What does MAT mean?

‚úÖ Medication Assisted Treatment
‚úÖ Treatment for substance use disorders
‚úÖ FDA-approved medications 
‚úÖ Counseling and behavioral therapies
‚úÖ The ‚ÄúWhole-patient‚Äù approach
